[No information is available regarding the incubation period between ingestion of the alleged food and onset of illness, what symptoms occurred (nausea, vomiting, and/or diarrhea), whether fever was present, and how long the illnesses lasted. This information can be quite useful in assessing possible etiology until test results are available.

ProMED would appreciate information from knowledgeable sources on the results of the investigation. - Mod.LL

